{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sent Nathan Clipper-- sent messengers,-- not he, through that general which sent soldiers in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, soldiers could go in and out, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and they came down to the community, and it was arranged that, not direct to the family branch then, because it was his father, and his mother, and the father, and the mother, and the brothers-- it was big families.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Clippers and the Bronsteins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was so done that-- you know, it was also what they call a Jewish-- you cannot call it Jewish federation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had to be something organized there in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they brought in whatever they could over there, and then it was the best distribute to anybody who need it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were aware of when it was-- oh, yeah-- when it was [NON-ENGLISH] and so, then, we had-- like, Passover, we had a big Passover-- double ration of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, we were a few kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew where potatoes in, you know, in the [? summer ?] were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So quietly, we had some old bucket, you know, with holes, with everything rusted out-- who cares-- went to that little farm, dug out with dirty hands these-- these potatoes, filled them up in the bucket, and brought it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had double ratio Passover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Never forget that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, I never forget, it was already bad when I was still home, in the '39 or '40 Passover.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, the sawmill, what we had, they-- they had to watch there is no sabotage or anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had rations, all kind of rations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had oil-- good oil.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I walk maybe five kilometers or so, and I said-- I watch what I did, a big boy.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
